A '''Committee of Adjustment''', similar to a Zoning Board of Adjustment, is a [[quasi-judicial body]] in each [[Ontario]] municipality that adjudicates matters related to minor variances to [[Zoning]] by-laws and [[Severance (land)|consents to severances of land]].

